	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Went safely among the Gauls to perform, according to Livy (5.46.1-3, and 52.3, with praenomen C.; Val. Max. 1.1.11), private family rites, but according to other sources, public rites as Pontifex (Cass. Hem. fr. 19 Peter, in App. Celt. 6; cf. Flor. 1.7.16; Dio fr. 25, with praenomen Caeso; Ampel. 20)." ;
	dprr:hasID 524 .
